ğŸ“œ STEP 2: Jenkinsfile (IMPORTANT)
This pipeline:
â€¢	pulls GitHub code
â€¢	copies file to EC2
â€¢	overwrites file in /opt
pipeline {
    agent any

    stages {
        stage('Clone Repo') {
            steps {
                git branch: 'main',
                    url: 'https://github.com/sowtheswari22/ec2-folder-automation.git'
            }
        }

        stage('Deploy File to EC2') {
            steps {
                sshagent(['ec2-key']) {
                    sh """
                    scp -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no hello_world.txt ubuntu@<EC2_PUBLIC_IP>:/opt/hello_world.txt
                    """
                }
            }
        }
    }
}
ğŸ” Replace:
â€¢	<EC2_PUBLIC_IP> with your EC2 public IP
â€¢	ec2-key â†’ Jenkins credential ID
Commit this Jenkinsfile.
